<br>
As a result, we have a set of gloves that give us 15ac, 20str, 10 to all stats/saves and 100hp. Plus an instaclickable song that provides ac, attack, and 40% song haste.<br>
<br>
Our epic is a weapon in that it turns our bare fists into 9/16 weapons (before haste), but as there are many other weapons with a better ratio, we can still equip them without losing any of the stats or effects from our epic.<br>
<br>
look around - you most likely will not see any L60 monks, including those in the most uber guild using anything other than Celestial Fists in the glove slot.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps<br>
